{ Trade or no trade? } 1. Nxe6
{ Trade! Wait, what? The White knight is glorious, the Black bishop is a piece of garbage, isn't it? Well, again, look at the remaining pieces. Argue the case of the a8 knight and you'll be laughed out of the room. The c6 pawn can be attacked more times than defended now, since the bishop is going to a4. Add to that the fact that now the Black queen has to blockade a passed pawn, a task that should be given to a weaker piece like the departed bishop. }
1... Qxe6 2. Rec1
{ Next is the tripling on the c-file or the penetration along the a-file. The brave knight has done well to sacrifice itself. }
