[SetUp "1"]

{ Now how does he acquire this control? } 1. d5
{ White kills off the b7 bishop, weakens the f5 pawn and softens up the e6 square. }
1... e5 2. Bc1 Nh7 3. Bh3
{ The pawn is falling. g6 is impossible as h6 would be hanging. } *

