[SetUp "1"]

{ No Square of Squares this time, only a serpentine c5-d4-e5-f4-g5. How does White claim an edge ? }
1. Ba3
{ The knight can't go to c5 anymore and White piles up the pressure in one of the key games of the 1963 World Championship. }
1... Rfe8 2. Rd4 Nb8 3. Rfd1 Rxd4 4. Rxd4 fxg3 5. hxg3 Qf7 6. Qe4 g6 7. Qh4
{ Black is going to lose his house and all the material inside it. } *

