[SetUp "1"]

{ Who is better and why? } 1... b6
{ Despite White having much more space and the optically better bishop, he actually stands worse because Black has all the levers at his disposal, from b6 to g5. White is already at full capacity but can't do anything constructive, while Black's pieces are at their lowest currently. }
2. Rc1 Re8 3. Bh3 h5 4. Bf1 g6 5. h3 h4 { Both wings will open up. } 6. g4 bxc5
7. dxc5 g5
{ Analyze this further to convince yourself that Black is indeed for choice. This is a very instructive case of too much space and too few pieces to control it. }
