{ The famous secret of the Soviet school of chess: if you have something to do, do it! }
2. dxe5 Nc5 3. Qe3 Bg4 4. exd6 Bxd6 5. Nd4 Rae8 6. Qd2 Be5
{ Black has fantastic activity, White can only continue } 7. f3 Bf5 8. Nxf5
Qxf5 9. Bxe5 Qxe5 10. Rab1 a4 11. bxa4 Qe3+ 12. Qxe3 Rxe3 13. Rfe1 Rfe8
