14. Rxe3 Rxe3 15. Kf2 Rxa3 16. Bh3 Rxa4 17. Ke3 Kf7
{ 30...Rxc4  31.Rxb7 !  Nxb7  32.Be6+ } 18. Kd4 Ra5
{ The endgame is now balanced. } *

